title: It isn’t over
author: VD
content_html:
Hillary isn’t in any trouble that she wasn’t in a few months ago. As I originally ended Monday’s column until the editor decided that he really didn’t need any more fireworks:

“Most of the experience political pundits have been counting out the Lizard Queen for months now. But as with any epic horror villain, it’s wise to refrain from assuming that she’s done until she’s been staked, beheaded, and her mouth stuffed with garlic.”

The delegate math is irrelevant. It always has been. I don’t take it any more seriously than last month’s CPI report.
